  <p>Hello! I'm Vipin — a developer based in Gurugram, India who writes about technology, productivity, and the art of living intentionally.</p>

  <p>This blog is my small corner of the internet. A place to think out loud, share what I'm learning, and explore ideas that don't fit neatly into a tweet. I write slowly and publish when something feels truly worth saying.</p>

  <p>By day I build software. By night I read, write, and wonder about how to build a life that actually means something.</p>

